}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "MADE IN TAIWAN", "4900K310", and "NEE 2M 94V-0" (etc, etc) is silkscreened on the board (which is essentially the same as the [[SerComm IP706ST]]'s board). :'''G-LUXON''' and '''Lelon''' radial capacitors are in use on a sample production board.
The FCC operational description states the devices uses TNETW5305 and ACX100. The Flash and RAM is stated as being 1MB and 4MB, respectively.. but with the possibility for upgrade from the OEM. :Per unit noted above, this is correct. The presumed TNETW5305 is marked '''CF74I553GGW'''<\n>'''C 3BACT JW'''.
According to the manual, the default SSID is '''NETGEAR'''.
